headline: CHIPOTLE MEXICAN GRILL TO ANNOUNCE SECOND QUARTER 2025 RESULTS ON JULY 23, 2025
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) will host a conference call on Wednesday, July 23, 2025 at 4:30 PM Eastern time to discuss second quarter 2025 financial results and provide a business update for the third quarter to date.
